<HEADLINE>
<P>
STUDENT LOANS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Regarding your editorial "Stemming Student Loan Defaults" (April 7), please let 
us encourage responsibility. When a student takes out a loan to help with his 
college education, he is making a commitment and a pledge to repay that loan! 
Go after the $2 billion in loans that are not being paid back! 
</P>
