Again, the "good guy" who is being responsible and pays his or her bills 
doesn't get any encouragement, but we're just supposed to find all kinds of 
excuses for acts of irresponsibility. We must restore values and promote 
responsibility or this generation of beautiful young people is doomed. Let us 
wake up before it is too late! 
</P>
<P>
HELEN LESKO ROGERS 
