practice, to defame me and my practice, that began before the recall attempt." 
; Photo, Robert L. Hansen: "The severe financial condition of the hospital is 
now open and obvious to all of the current board of directors, whose duty it is 
to correct the condition." ; Photo, Larry Orosz: "The board has not done a 
perfect job, but it is willing to learn. This is better than replacing them 
with others that we do not know." 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
