<HEADLINE>
<P>
SAN DIEGO EARNINGS: SAN DIEGO COUNTY 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 DH Technology, a manufacturer of computer print heads, reported a 
first-quarter profit of $1.2 million on sales of $9.5 million, up from a profit 
of $175,000 on sales of $3 million for the same quarter a year earlier. 
</P>
<P>
DH Technology attributed the improvements to increased shipments of its 
products and to the inclusion of results from its acquisition last year of 
Eaton Printer products, since renamed DHPrint. 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
<P>
