</P>
<P>
COMMUNITY TASK FORCE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Los Angeles Councilwoman Ruth Galanter has named a 15-member community task 
force in the Crenshaw-Baldwin Hills area to study issues affecting the elderly. 
The group, which will meet quarterly, will advise the councilwoman in 
implementing community projects and programs for senior citizens. 
</P>
