<P>
Photo, Set play -- Matt Sonnichsen of UCLA makes pass as teammate Mike Whitcomb 
(30) covers and CSULB's Mike Kerins prepares to defend. WENDY LAMM / Los 
Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
