<P>
Wild Art 
</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA042089-0200 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 46694 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
April 20, 1989, Thursday, Orange County P.M. Final 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Part A; Page 1; Column 4; Late Final Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<GRAPHIC>
<P>
Photo, 'I'm guilty' -- Confessed killer Ramon Salcido appears on camera in an 
interview on the private Televisa network in Mazatlan. Salcido, suspected of 
killing seven family members in Sonoma County, Calif., said: "I did the 
killings in the United States. I expect to be judged there." (Story in Part I, 
